---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Australian Math Coach – Personalised Maths Tutoring" description="Online and in-person maths coaching for Australian students, plus a companion practice app to keep skills sharp.">
  <section id="hero" class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-[90vw] mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_auto] gap-12 items-center">
      <div data-reveal class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-purple-100/70 rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-2xl">
        <p class="uppercase tracking-widest text-sm text-purple-600 font-semibold mb-3">Australian Math Coach</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-6">
          Flexible maths coaching for ambitious students across Australia
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Personalised one-on-one tutoring delivered online from Brisbane (with local in-person sessions around the western suburbs on request).
          We help students master concepts, prepare for exams, and rebuild confidence from Year 5 through university bridging courses.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary text-base px-10 py-4 text-center">Book a free consultation</a>
          <a href="#services" class="btn-secondary text-base px-10 py-4 text-center">Explore coaching paths</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal class="hidden lg:flex flex-col gap-4 text-right text-gray-700">
        <div class="bg-white/70 border border-purple-100 rounded-2xl py-6 px-8 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-purple-600">98%</p>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500">Students who improved two grade bands or more</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/70 border border-pink-100 rounded-2xl py-6 px-8 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-pink-500">Year 5 – VCE</p>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500">Curriculum-aligned lessons &amp; exam coaching</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/70 border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl py-6 px-8 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-500">10+ yrs</p>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500">Professional tutoring experience</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services" class="py-24 bg-white/90">
    <div class="max-w-[90vw] mx-auto">
      <div data-reveal class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Coaching paths tailored to each stage</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          Whether we meet online or in person, every learning plan is built around the student's curriculum, goals, and confidence level.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
        <article data-reveal class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-purple-100 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Foundation Boost (Years 5–8)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Strengthen number sense, fractions, and problem solving. Ideal for students who need a confidence reset or enrichment beyond classwork.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>✔ Weekly 60-minute lessons</li>
            <li>✔ Parent-friendly progress snapshots</li>
            <li>✔ Optional in-person catch-ups around Brisbane</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="mt-auto text-sm font-semibold text-purple-600 uppercase tracking-wide">From $70 per session</span>
        </article>
        <article data-reveal class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-blue-100 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">High School Success (Years 9–12)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Keep pace with coursework, plug any gaps, and build exam confidence for VCE General, Methods, and Specialist Mathematics.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>✔ Custom study schedules plus exam-style practice</li>
            <li>✔ Feedback loops that focus on thinking process</li>
            <li>✔ Intensive revision blocks before assessments</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="mt-auto text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wide">From $85 per session</span>
        </article>
        <article data-reveal class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Exam &amp; Bridge Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">University preparation, mature-age entry maths refreshers, and targeted support for national tests such as NAPLAN or UCAT quant.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>✔ Diagnostic start session with action plan</li>
            <li>✔ Weekly accountability check-ins</li>
            <li>✔ Access to curated question banks</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="mt-auto text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide">Programs from 4 weeks</span>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="approach" class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[90vw] mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1fr] gap-12 items-start">
      <div data-reveal class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-xl p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">How a coaching block unfolds</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-6 text-gray-600">
          <li>
            <span class="block text-purple-600 font-semibold uppercase text-sm mb-1">1. Discover</span>
            We meet virtually to learn about the student's goals, school schedule, and sticking points. Baseline tasks help us map the first wins.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="block text-purple-600 font-semibold uppercase text-sm mb-1">2. Customise</span>
            Lessons combine clear explanations, interactive practice, and exam-style questions that match the current syllabus.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="block text-purple-600 font-semibold uppercase text-sm mb-1">3. Reinforce</span>
            Between sessions we set micro-practice challenges, guided reflections, and quick check-ins to lock in progress.
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div data-reveal class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 via-white to-blue-50 border border-purple-100 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Online-first, local when it helps</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Zoom-based sessions keep scheduling easy for families anywhere in Australia. Students around Brisbane can add occasional in-person workshops for exam intensives or tricky topics.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 via-white to-amber-50 border border-pink-100 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Transparent feedback for families</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Every block finishes with a short progress summary, next-focus recommendations, and take-home strategies so parents stay in the loop.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="results" class="py-24 bg-white/90">
    <div class="max-w-[90vw] mx-auto">
      <div data-reveal class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Real outcomes from real students</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">From students who feared maths to those chasing top-band scores, we focus on measurable wins.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div data-reveal class="bg-white border border-purple-100 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl">
          <p class="text-5xl font-black text-purple-600 mb-2">6 → 9</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Year 10 student lifted their NAPLAN band in two terms with weekly online sessions and targeted practice sets.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="bg-white border border-blue-100 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl">
          <p class="text-5xl font-black text-blue-500 mb-2">ATAR +11</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">VCE Methods student boosted their predicted ATAR by eleven points after a structured 12-week sprint.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal class="bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl">
          <p class="text-5xl font-black text-emerald-500 mb-2">5 ★</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Families rate our coaching 5/5 for communication, clarity, and the way we restore confidence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="app" class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-[90vw] mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.9fr] gap-12 items-center">
      <div data-reveal class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-pink-500 text-white rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-2xl">
        <p class="uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.3em] mb-3 text-white/70">New • Practice Resource</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4">Introducing the AMC Problem Lab</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/90 mb-6">
          A growing collection of interactive problem sets that reinforce what we cover in coaching. Launch tricky algebra drills, visualise calculus ideas, and review step-by-step solutions.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-white/80 mb-8">
          <li>• Curated to match Australian syllabi</li>
          <li>• Smart hints that guide thinking without giving the answer</li>
          <li>• Track streaks and share progress with your coach</li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="https://app.australianmathcoach.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-purple-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition"
        >
          Visit the Problem Lab
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal class="bg-white/80 border border-purple-100 rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-xl">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Coming soon for subscribers</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Right now the Lab is free for coaching students while we add more content. Later this year it will be available as a low-cost monthly subscription for independent learners.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Want early access without coaching?</p>
            <p>Join the waitlist when you book a consultation or send us an email—beta slots open soon.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Educator or school program?</p>
            <p>Ask about bulk licences and co-branded practice sets tailored to your curriculum maps.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 via-pink-600 to-blue-600 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-[90vw] mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.85fr] gap-12 items-start">
      <div data-reveal class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black">Let's build a plan together</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/90">
          Tell us about the student, their current year level, and what success looks like. We respond within one business day with suggested session times and next steps.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-white/80">
          <p><i class="fas fa-phone mr-3"></i> <a href="tel:+61418764798" class="hover:text-white">0418 764 798</a></p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-envelope mr-3"></i> <a href="mailto:info@australianmathcoach.com" class="hover:text-white">info@australianmathcoach.com</a></p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-location-dot mr-3"></i> 6 Turner Street, Corinda, Brisbane Q4075</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal class="bg-white/95 rounded-3xl p-8 text-gray-800 shadow-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Quick enquiry form</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">No spam—just a friendly reply with availability and a short plan.</p>
        <form
          class="space-y-4"
          action="https://formsubmit.co/info@australianmathcoach.com"
          method="POST"
          target="_blank"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Australian Math Coach enquiry" />
          <div>
            <label for="name" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 block mb-1">Parent or guardian name *</label>
            <input id="name" name="name" required class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500" placeholder="Alex Taylor" />
          </div>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 block mb-1">Email *</label>
              <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500" placeholder="name@example.com" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="phone" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 block mb-1">Phone</label>
              <input id="phone" name="phone" class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500" placeholder="Optional" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <label for="student" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 block mb-1">Student first name *</label>
              <input id="student" name="student" required class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500" placeholder="Jamie" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="year-level" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 block mb-1">Year level *</label>
              <input id="year-level" name="year level" required class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500" placeholder="Year 10" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="goals" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 block mb-1">Goals or challenges *</label>
            <textarea id="goals" name="goals" rows="4" required class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500" placeholder="Tell us how we can help"></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="w-full btn-primary py-4 text-base font-semibold text-center">Send enquiry</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
